## ğŸ”‘ Best Practices
- Donâ€™t use **3D charts** â€” they look flashy but confuse interpretation.  
- Use **pie charts wisely** â€” only when values sum to a whole.  
- Avoid **misleading graphs** â€” clarity is more important than style.  
- Donâ€™t **over-graph** â€” break complex visuals into simpler parts:contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}.  

